  <h1>What is Haskell? A clear introduction</h1>
  <div class="artmeta"><span>By Coldwast</span><span>Updated Jun 14, 2026</span><span>7 min read</span><span class="tag">#haskell</span><span class="tag">#functional</span><span class="tag">#intro</span></div>
